        "html": "<p>Hello {first_name, \"there\"},</p><p>I've been heads down for the last few days, working on the piece I really wanted to write about TikTok, and I finally got it finished and published this morning. Even if you're not really interested in the platform, please do give it a read. It's just as much about how we should handle publishing on social platforms as it is about the specific problems that TikTok itself creates.</p><p>Now that's done, it's back to normal service this week ‚Äî and hopefully finishing that series on community I started last week. But first, let's talk TikTok, the BBC and China‚Ä¶</p>"
